name: sslprotect.js
tagline: Weak protection against tools like sslstrip
body:
### Security Warning
You have been redirected to this site for security reasons.
The website you just visited should be secured by SSL, but was sent unencrypted.  
This could mean that your network connection has been hijacked.  
Please consult your local administrator or contact the site owner.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
